<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.6.8">
<l>vētam vallār kaḷaikkoṇṭu viṇṇōr perumāṉṟirup</l>
<l>pātam paṇintiva ṇōyitu tīrttuk koḷḷātupō</l>
<l>yētam paṟaintalla ceytu kaḷḷūṭu kalāyttūyk</l>
<l>kīta muḻaviṭṭu nīraṇaṅ kāṭutal kīḻmaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without ending yourself this pain of her’s by  bowing before the auspicious</l>
<l>feet of the great lord of the celestials, taking those who master the Veda, your</l>
<l>going [and], talking of blame, committing sins, mixing [and] sprinkling toddy</l>
<l>in between, setting up drums for song [and] dancing as demonesses</l>
	<l>[is] baseness.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
